{"tid":35304,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【特首選戰】消息指曾俊華已向梁特請辭","createTime":"2016-12-12T04:18:11.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-12T05:56:09.000Z","uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8ec48b5e9a8a857689df6bc99136ba85293095f2","tid":35304,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T04:18:11.000Z","msg":"有線新聞引述消息指，表明考慮參選特首的財政司司長曾俊華，已向特首梁振英請辭。財爺日前以《有你同行》為題寫網誌，回顧在財政司9年半的工作，特意借小故事帶出任內政績。政界有傳曾俊華會在一兩日內正式辭職，最快於選委會投票結果出爐後便宣佈參選。  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20161212/56036408\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20161212%2F56036408&d=k2qU4R8jusNkkBkMdQvYkAT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=898497f9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20161212%2F56036408&h=45688cf6\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20161212/56036408</a>"},{"pid":"806ebf31abdac1789a254c94ec6dc7bfda50c9fb","tid":35304,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T04:18:37.000Z","msg":"品客GOGOGO<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09804c87457d84ad213546503c1e2a978a1d2dea","tid":35304,"uid":14188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T05:29:10.000Z","msg":"收皮啦想同我鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d99e6ed9173591e8d700c24a9540ddef051e68f4","tid":35304,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T05:56:09.000Z","msg":"5毛普遍回應、幫港出聲，港人講地<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c660P2W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc660P2W.jpg&h=37d060e3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/67K8Yq8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F67K8Yq8.jpg&h=5b09dbd6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A17wbW8.jpg\" data-thumbna